title: Fannie, Freddie Stock Woes Deepen as IPO Questions Mount
description: Shares of Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac extended days-long losing streaks amid mounting unease about the impact of President Donald Trump’s policy moves on efforts to release the mortgage-finance giants from government control.
